cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.SY, cs.LG

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper presents a framework for autonomous estimation of deformability distribution map of heterogeneous elastic surfaces using a robotic arm and sensor. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper uses a PrimeSense camera for environmental observations. 
- cs.GR (Graphics): The paper uses Position-based Dynamics simulator for modeling the elastic behavior of portions of the environment. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper presents a probabilistic framework for modeling deformable surfaces. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses Gaussian Processes for constructing a model of the environment geometry and for mapping the local deformability on the whole environment.
